file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: test
  version: '1.0'
servers:
  - url: 'http://localhost:3000'
paths:
  /postModel:
    post:
      summary: Create New User
      operationId: post-user
      responses:
        '200':
          description: User Created
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/User'
              examples: {}
        '400':
          description: Missing Required Information
      description: Create a new user.
      requestBody:
        content:
          multipart/form-data:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/Request'
    parameters: []
components:
  schemas:
    User:
      title: User
      type: object
      description: ''
      x-examples: {}
      properties:
        integerValue:
          type: integer
    Request:
      title: Request
      type: object
      properties:
        user1:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/User'
